QP arrived at the clients home at the scheduled time. QP discussed problems and concerns.  QP explained to client the importance of having patience when trying to regain financial stability. QP also assisted the client with completing apartment applications promptly. QP expressed the importance of remaining focused on the search for housing with the client.  QP educated the client of the importance of finding housing and remaining away from his friends on the street. QP educated the  client some activities he would like to engage in to help him with making progress towards him financial goals. QP suggested client to research an activity he would like to engage in that will help him with improving his cognitive and behavioral strategies. QP assisted client with researching how to prioritize funds and monthly bills. QP demonstrated for client how to put monthly expenses in order to show the client how to approach how saving and spending is important in the future.
